Gerald Mohr https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gerald_Mohr 0 Gerald Mohr (June 11, 1914 – November 9, 1968) was an American radio, film, and television character actor and frequent leading man, who appeared in more than 500 radio plays, 73 films, and over 100 television shows.
